         <abstract id="aspace_639997fdefcd0b91c7cf117e6bf364bd">Thirteen hours of interviews, done in 2001-2002 by Justin Ruben, with Edward Grant, New Haven African-American activist; photocopies of Ruben's interview notes; and "The Sometimes Angry Not So Young Black Man of New Haven," a paper written by Ruben for History 454a (graduate course in American history), based on the Grant interviews.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="local">
               <part>Ruben, Justin</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
